\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Hyperparameter tuning for the congestion predictor. Training and validation loss quickly flatten, and the lowest validation loss occurs at 60 epochs. The highlighted 30-epoch checkpoint is selected by downstream utility, not by validation loss: it yields about 7.1\% mean throughput improvement versus only about 1.6\% at 60 epochs. Predictor quality and scheduler utility are therefore misaligned.}}{3}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:hyper}{{1}{3}{Hyperparameter tuning for the congestion predictor. Training and validation loss quickly flatten, and the lowest validation loss occurs at 60 epochs. The highlighted 30-epoch checkpoint is selected by downstream utility, not by validation loss: it yields about 7.1\% mean throughput improvement versus only about 1.6\% at 60 epochs. Predictor quality and scheduler utility are therefore misaligned}{figure.1}{}}
\newlabel{fig:hyper@cref}{{[figure][1][]1}{[1][3][]3}{}{}{}}
